::Killfest/Demise/EndBringer/Scyther/Greven::

Killfest nearly falls forward as Megantron slams into him, water and 
ice nearly hitting him but missing. He growls, reaching back and 
throwing Megatron off him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Demise smashes through a tree, seeing Marine firing at EndBringer and 
charging at the bot, swinging his claws at his back.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
EndBringer doubles over, nearly coughing his 'lungs' out as he 
inhales the gas. He jumps back, firing rather blindly at Tankorr with 
several missiles.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther turns sharply around, several bolts nearly hitting him. He 
flies as fast as he can away from the energonians, wanting to lose 
them.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Greven trips on a rock, falling and spinning so that the cluster 
missiles would hit Aerostreak. He wanted the bot off. Greven didn't 
appreciate being chocked, but he could go on without air for a little 
while.
